00:05:08.279 --> 00:05:09.240
Fine.

00:05:09.240 --> 00:05:10.720
I'll remember you.

00:05:34.720 --> 00:05:36.959
What are you afraid of?

00:05:36.959 --> 00:05:38.199
Shouldn't you thank me?

00:05:41.160 --> 00:05:41.920
Gesang Deji,

00:05:43.720 --> 00:05:44.959
