00:05:46.439 --> 00:05:47.720
In death, you'll be my ghost.

00:05:57.120 --> 00:05:57.920
Sister!

00:06:05.439 --> 00:06:06.120
Deji!

00:06:08.399 --> 00:06:09.399
Sister!

00:06:10.160 --> 00:06:11.040
From the moment we were born,

00:06:11.040 --> 00:06:14.079
